{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "第十九回\"脱困的方法\"讲述了陆小凤逃离宫九追击的过程。清晨，西门吹雪以惊人剑术刺死宫九的马，为陆小凤争取逃跑时间。宫九被西门吹雪的杀气所慑，不敢轻举妄动。陆小凤逃出后担心西门吹雪安危，毅然返回寻找。西门吹雪安然无恙，两人重逢叙旧。西门吹雪告知宫九因被牛肉汤鞭打而丑态百出，令其作呕。西门吹雪决定让陆小凤住在他家躲避，自己则去学佛。与此同时，十二连环坞总瓢把子鹰眼老七奉宫九之命率二十人前来暗杀西门吹雪，但内心充满挣扎与不安。陆小凤发现鹰眼老七的行踪，决定暗中监视保护西门吹雪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你为什么要杀我的马？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我不希望你的马追上我的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "假如我要追呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "你的人，就会和你的马一样下场。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你有自信吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "西门吹雪是江湖上最有自信的人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "你要不要试一试？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你在凭吊那匹马？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "这不是你的血？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是的话，我还会站在这里吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "哦，对，这是马的血。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么要赶回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "我害怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你害怕我会遭宫九的毒手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就凭你这点，你以后来找我办事，我不要你剃胡子了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你确实让我担上了心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你以为我会死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "因为你是个极爱清洁的人，岂能容许一滩血在你屋前？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我当然不能容忍，只是我没有时间去清洗。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你没有时间？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是的，我还未来得及清洗，你就来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "我来以前呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我正在河边吐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "吐？呕吐？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你为什么要吐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我见到一个人，他的举动丑陋得令我非吐不可。",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "宫九。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "宫九？他怎么啦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他哀求我打他。",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你打了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有。高手过招前的凝视，绝不能疏忽，我以为他是故意扰乱我的注意力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "然后他忽然举起手来，自己打自己的脸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你还是没有理他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说对了。我依旧目不转睛地看着他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "他怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他挨了鞭子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "挨谁的鞭子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "牛肉汤的。牛肉汤不停的打他，他在地上翻滚，高兴得大叫。",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我赶快冲到河边，大吐特吐，要不然……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "要不然就怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "要不然我吐在地上，这里我就不能再住了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "那恐怕我就要赔你一栋房子了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知道我这栋房子价值多少吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "值多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知道霍休吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你猜错了。",
      "tone": "否定",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "我猜错了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只不过是说，任何一栋房子，都是无价的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为房子里的人，也许有一天也会名动四方的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你说得一点也不错，霍老头的那栋木屋，在陆放翁行吟的时候，根本也只不过是一堆木头盖起来的房子而已，但是陆放翁的诗受到世人的赏识以后，到了霍老头住的时候，就价值连城了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以假如我不能住在这里，这种房子你也赔不起。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你错了，我赔得起。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "因为我现在根本不必赔给你，等几百年后，后世的人都还知道有个西门吹雪的时候，我已经羽化登仙去了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我发现你会耍赖。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算是吧，也赖不到你身上，因为你现在根本不会搬走。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "这次是你错了。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我马上就要搬走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为，这里适合你住。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "适合我住？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "宫九一定以为你已经走了，怎么也想不到你还会回来，所以他不管派出多少耳目，不管他的耳目在哪里探听，都再也打听不到你的行踪。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "因为我已经在你这里高枕无忧了。",
      "tone": "恍然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "完全正确。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "那么你呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你去哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我去学佛。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "学佛？跟谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然跟和尚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "跟哪一位和尚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "老实和尚！",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "老实和尚懂佛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你不知道？你不知道还要跟他学？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只跟他学一招。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "哪一招？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "坐怀不乱。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "坐怀不乱？学来干什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "学来对着两个大美人的时候，不会心猿意马。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "两个大美人又是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一个叫沙曼，一个叫小玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "你是说，你要去接他们来这里？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你有比这更安全更好的方法吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "请说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "只是我们暂时都做不到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "speaker_name": "西门吹雪",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那是什么方法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_chui_xue",
      "text": "杀死宫九的方法。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱哥儿俩今天晚上去翻翻本，然后再去找春红和桃娘乐上一乐如何？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "翻你个大头鬼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么啦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "你知道我生平最怕的一件事是什么吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "就是摸门钉。有一次我去办事，也是找不到人，结果我去推了几把牌九，哈，你知道结果吗？连续二十七把，我拿的都是炮十。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你今天没看到西门吹雪，你就不赌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "绝不赌。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我劝你还是痛痛快快赌一场的好。",
      "tone": "劝告",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你见到西门吹雪，恐怕就不一定有机会赌了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "你是说我们杀不了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只怕是没有可能。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "不可能。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那么自信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "当然，我们二十个人在他全无提防之下，忽然发了二十种不同的暗器，我看神仙恐怕也难躲得过，何况只不过是凡人而已。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    }
